Become briefly untargetable and dive-bomb into the largest group of enemies, dealing 80/150/1500(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage in a 3-hex circle and Stunning for 1.25/1.25/10 seconds. After landing, cast Flame Breath immediately.

Flame Breath: Breathe fire in a cone, dealing up to 700/1200/20000(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to enemies hit. While breathing fire, is always enraged.

skill.name: Crystalline Exoskeleton
skill.desc: Gain 300/375/450(%i:scaleAP%) Shield for 8 seconds and 160/180/200% Attack Speed while it holds.

skill.name: Tideblossom
skill.desc:
Mark an unmarked enemy, dealing 200/300/1200(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to enemies along the way. Marks transfer to a nearby enemy on Mark owner death.

After 3 casts, the next cast deals 335/505/1800(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage in a 2-hex radius around all marked enemies.

skill.name: Starfall
skill.desc:
Passive: While any ally is below 50% Health, gain an additional 15 mana per attack.

Active: Call down a shower of 14 stars over the next 2 seconds. Allies are healed for 105/165/1000(%i:scaleAP%) each time a star hits them.

skill.name: Dragon Master's Decree
skill.desc: Launch 8 dragonlings toward nearby enemies. Each deals 90/130/600(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to their target, then returns to restore for 12% missing Health.

skill.name: Rampage
skill.desc:
Charge toward the farthest enemy within 2.5 hexes, dealing 145/220/850(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage and Stunning enemies hit.

Then bite an enemy, dealing 350/525/1800(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage and ignoring 33%(%i:scaleAP%) of the target's Armor.

skill.name: Petricite Burst
skill.desc:
Deal 140/200/320(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to nearby enemies and gain 365/415/525(%i:scaleAP%) Shield for 6 seconds. If Shield is already active, hit a larger area and 30% Mana Reave enemies struck.

Mana Reave: Increase Ability cost until next cast

skill.name: Flowing Volley
skill.desc: Throw 3 stones towards the current target, each dealing 170/255/385(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to the first enemy hit.

skill.name: Earthquake
skill.desc:
Stomp three times, creating a surrounding earthquake that deals 460/640/5360(%i:scaleArmor%%i:scaleMR%%i:scaleAD%) physical damage. When it ends, gain 130/165/4000(%i:scaleAP%) Armor and Magic Resist for 8 seconds. While casting, become Unstoppable.

Unstoppable: Gain immunity to crowd control

skill.name: Explosive Charge
skill.desc:
Passive: Grants Nomsy 50/75/120% Attack Damage.

Active: Places 1 explosive charges, prioritizing the nearby targets without a charge. Charges detonate after 1 second(s), dealing 130/160/200(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage to nearby enemies and 85/155/285(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to the target.

skill.name: Blast Potion
skill.desc:
Deal 130/210/345(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage to enemies in a 1-hex radius centered on the target and 20% Sunder them for 5 seconds.

Sunder: Reduce Armor

skill.name: Chain of Constellations
skill.desc: Shoot a tendril towards the current target, dealing 170/255/475(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage to the first enemy hit and Stunning them for 1 seconds. It then spreads to 3 nearby enemies, dealing 155/255/405(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage and Stunning them for the same duration.

skill.name: Transfusion
skill.desc: Heal 275/325/375(%i:scaleAP%) and deal 275/325/375(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to the target.

skill.name: Relentless Storm
skill.desc: Gain 500/800/1200 max Health. For the rest of combat, every 3rd attack deals 100/140/240(%i:scaleAP%) bonus magic damage to the target, and 100/140/240(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to up to 4 additional enemies.

skill.name: Feathers FLY!
skill.desc:
For 4 seconds, attacks leave a feather behind the target and 2 nearby enemies.

At the end of this duration, recall all feathers, dealing 24/35/103(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage per feather to enemies struck.

skill.name: Sweeping Blade
skill.desc:
Gain 180/240/2500(%i:scaleAP%) Shield for 2 seconds and dash through the target, slashing nearby enemies for 135/245/6000(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage.

Every third cast the slash deals 250% damage, hits a larger area, and Stuns enemies for 1.5 seconds. If only one enemy remains, repeatedly slash them until they die.

skill.name: Way of the Hunter
skill.desc: Passive: Attacks alternate between dealing 85/125/180(%i:scaleAP%) bonus magic damage and dealing 15(%i:scaleAD%) bonus physical damage.

skill.name: Unstable Current
skill.desc: Restore 250/285/340(%i:scaleAP%) Health and explode outwards towards enemies within 2 hexes, dealing 10%/12%/18% of their max Health as magic damage.

skill.name: Watershock Laser
skill.desc: Fire a water pulse at the closest enemy within 3 hexes, or at the centermost enemy, Stunning them for 0.75 seconds. When the pulse explodes it deals 70/110/175(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage and creates a laser behind the target that deals 275/375/525(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to all enemies hit.

skill.name: Somersault Assault
skill.desc: Gain 375/450/650(%i:scaleAP%) Shield for 2 seconds and deal 340/540/1050(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage to the highest percent health enemy, Stunning and knocking them back slightly.

skill.name: Spell Thief
skill.desc: Nab an Ability from another dimension and cast it.

skill.name: Grasping Spines
skill.desc: Summon vines in the row with the most enemies, dealing 225/325/550(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage and Stunning them for 1 second(s).

skill.name: Maximum Grit Overdrive
skill.desc:
Over a short duration, heal 392/573/1928(%i:scaleHealth%%i:scaleAP%) and deal 140/210/2000(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage to the target.

Then, deal 164/259/893(%i:scaleHealth%%i:scaleAD%) physical damage in a cone. Enemies in the center line take 10/15/45 more physical damage, increased based on healing received this combat.

skill.name: Power Suit: Full Charge
skill.desc: Shield 400/475/575(%i:scaleAP%) for 4 seconds. The next 3 attacks deal 34/52/79(%i:scaleMR%) bonus true damage.

skill.name: Star Cutter
skill.desc: Launch a returning blade 2-hexes through the current target. It deals 190/285/430(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage to enemies hit, reduced by 40% per hit.

skill.name: Burn Blast
skill.desc:
Passive: Damage Burns and Wounds for 5 seconds. Ignore 30% of the target's Armor.

Active: Deal 290/435/700(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage to the target, and 50/75/120(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to the 3 nearest targets. Every 2 casts, fire a second blast at the next closest enemy, dealing 75% damage.

Burn: Deal 1% of the target's max Health as true damage every second
Wound: Reduce healing received by 33%

skill.name: Glittering Plumage Regalia
skill.desc:
Gain 395/511/688(%i:scaleHealth%%i:scaleAP%) max Health, then deal 25/35/55(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage every second to enemies in a 2-hex radius.

Subsequent casts heal 395/511/688(%i:scaleHealth%%i:scaleAP%) and increase the damage by 6/9/14(%i:scaleAP%).

skill.name: Bright Star Blast
skill.desc: Deal 215/325/485(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to the target and reduces their Magic Resist by 10.

skill.name: 52 Card Calamity
skill.desc:
Passive: Attacks bounce between 3 enemies, dealing 35/55/999(%i:scaleAP%) bonus magic damage and marking enemies hit. Attacks deal 30% reduced damage per hit.

Active: Deal 230/350/9999(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage to the 4 closest enemies, and detonate their marks for 15/25/500(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage each.

skill.name: Blazing Phoenix Stance
skill.desc: Make 3 rapid attacks. Each heals Udyr for 150/190/250(%i:scaleAP%) and deals 35/50/80(%i:scaleAD%) additional damage to enemies in a 1-hex radius.

skill.name: Level Zero: 100 Shot Demon
skill.desc:
Passive: Gain mana when units die. Enemies grant 5, allies 3.

Active: Fire 3(%i:scaleAS%) piercing arrows per second at random enemies until Varus is out of mana. Each arrow costs 12 mana and deals 100/150/866(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage, reduced by 35% per hit.

skill.name: Shining Knuckle Explosion
skill.desc:
Passive: Gain 2 %i:scaleArmor%%i:scaleMR% for each component equipped to your team.

Active: Heal 230/280/330(%i:scaleAP%), deal 150/225/350(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage in a 1-hex radius centered on the target, and 20% Sunder enemies hit for 4 seconds.

Sunder: Reduce Armor

skill.name: Combo of the Ruined King
skill.desc:
Passive: Attacks deal 60/90/148(%i:TFTBaseAD%%i:scaleAP%) magic damage.

Active: The next three attacks unleash a devastating combo.

Pommel Bash: Deal 100/150/270(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage.
Rising Slash: Deal 100/150/270(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage and briefly Stun the target.
Falling Slash: Deal 210/315/560(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage.

skill.name: Ursine Instinct
skill.desc:
Passive: Every 4th attack deals 125/190/750(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage in a 1-hex radius centered on the target. When changing targets, immediately slam for 70% damage.

Active: For 5 seconds gain 125%/125%/500% Attack Speed, 10/10/25%(%i:scaleAP%) Omnivamp, and crowd control immunity.

skill.name: Sharp Feathers Shine
skill.desc: Gain 80%(%i:scaleAP%) attack speed for 3 attacks. These attacks deal 50/75/115(%i:scaleAD%) bonus physical damage to the target and 2 nearby enemies

skill.name: Guarding Crescent
skill.desc: Heal 290/360/450(%i:scaleAP%), deal 100/150/235(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage to enemies in a 2-hex radius, and mark the current target. For 3 seconds, take 40% reduced damage from unmarked enemies.

skill.name: Unsheath the Storm
skill.desc: Deal 170/255/405(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage to the 3 closest enemies.

skill.name: Dual Blade Technique: Inner Reflection
skill.desc:
Passive: Attacks grant 5/5/25% stacking Attack Speed and Movement Speed, and alternate between dealing 25/40/400(%i:scaleAD%) bonus true damage and 100/160/999(%i:scaleAP%) bonus magic damage.

Active: Send an echo towards the two furthest enemies, dealing 140/210/9999(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage and briefly Stunning enemies hit.

skill.name: Read Or Die
skill.desc:
Launch 20 pages dealing 26/40/150(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage each, split between the target and enemies within 2 hexes. Each subsequent cast launches 4 more pages.

Potential (?%i:set14AmpIcon%): Every 4 pages, launch a bonus page that deals 36/56/210(%i:set14AmpIcon%%i:scaleAP%) true damage.

skill.name: Reality Ripple
skill.desc: Heal 240/280/350(%i:scaleAP%) and deal 146/232/372(%i:scaleAP%%i:scaleHealth%) magic damage to enemies within a 1-hex radius.

skill.name: Orbital Ordinance
skill.desc:
Passive: Attacks are bouncing bombs that deal 70/105/165(%i:scaleAP%%i:TFTBaseAD%) magic damage to the first enemy hit.

Active: Deal 230/345/550(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage in a 1-hex radius centered on the target.

skill.name: Crystal Thorn Expansion
skill.desc:
Summon 4/4/20 untargetable Thornspitters that deal 90/135/999(%i:scaleAP%) per attack and attack 4 times.

Non-plant allies gain 35%/50%/1009%(%i:scaleAP%) Attack Speed decaying over 4 seconds.

skill.name: Crystal Barbs
skill.desc: Attacks deal 70/105/500(%i:scaleAP%) bonus magic damage.

skill.name: Crystal Barbs
skill.desc: Attacks deal 90/135/500(%i:scaleAP%) bonus magic damage.
